com.att.research.xacml.std.datatypes

Class PortRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.std.datatypes.PortRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticString

    public final class PortRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements SemanticString
    PortRange represents the optional range of port values for an IPAddress. A value of -1 for either port represents the limit for port numbers (min or max) in the given addressing scheme.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.1 $
    Author:
